title: Curious George (PBS Kids) Season 8, Episodes 4-6
description:
Curious George is an animated television series based on the Curious George children's book series, which features Jeff Bennett as the voice of The Man with the Yellow Hat. Frank Welker, who voiced George in the 2006 feature film, returns here as the voice of Curious George. The show is currently broadcast on PBS Kids.


When the show was developed, educational advisers suggested using it to teach science, math, and engineering concepts. Episodes are often structured around a "try-fail" series of incidents, which proved to be a good way to show scientific inquiries. 


Here's the the second half of season 8, which aired in May 2014. These were encoded by me, from my digital recordings off my local PBS station. These may be the final episodes of Curious George, unless it gets renewed for a ninth season...if it does, new episodes may air in 2015.
